    new "Guess they brought you over later."

    old "Sarah held her face firm."
    new "Sarah held her face firm."

    old "Everyone who comes here to Al Gahaem is so sad at first."
    new "Everyone who comes here to Al Gahaem is so sad at first."

    old "And they think their tears will never run dry."
    new "And they think their tears will never run dry."

