    new "But say one thing about people, they can learn and adapt to just about anything."

    old "The girl spun around, running her hand across the surface of the water."
    new "The girl spun around, running her hand across the surface of the water."

    old "That's what the Tribesmen understand that nobody else understands in this world."
    new "That's what the Tribesmen understand that nobody else understands in this world."

    old "People think they can't ever be slaves, but if you discipline them well enough, every man or woman got it in them to be a slave."
