    new "Naydeen is the Khan's first wife. You a princess. Ayaka used to be a noble's daughter."

    old "But I just grew up a normal girl, never got not titles or gold the day I was born."
    new "But I just grew up a normal girl, never got not titles or gold the day I was born."

    old "In between the border of the desert and the empires of the Far East, there runs a long stretch of green pastures."
    new "In between the border of the desert and the empires of the Far East, there runs a long stretch of green pastures."

